/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係睇完你張圖突然有個idea諗到 <br />\n你電腦背面啲牆紙都有啲舊 但換又好煩<br />\n同一大面空白<br />\n會唔會買個大相框裝張靚既相上去裝飾下？<br />\n感覺會靚啲同養眼啲<br />\n又無咁單調<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DP9raaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDP9raaF.png&h=ccbd2539&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pefqqJ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpefqqJ1.png&h=320316c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n者係類似呢啲<br />\n或者一張靚既風景大圖 配一個大相框掛牆<br />\n都幾有feel"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"絕對又諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢種係咪要鑽牆 聽屋企人講牆好薄<br />\n我有諗過加個架放CD貼牆做幅2-3隻CD高既'牆'出黎<br />\n又或者裝個架放氣槍<br />\n成日一得閒就諗點加點加 但係太煩最後都冇搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗架有啲好似<br />\n而家有啲無痕貼紙呀<br />\n多重吸力設計定唔知咩個啲相框都有<br />\n我自己影開相都有諗過係間房整啲靚相框放自己中諗意既作品<br />\n不過間房未大執所以一直都未搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fc9170728c41439fe7a8930ff0422a1715078d","tid":1171201,"uid":119337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b1f84ff0c9cf12b47ab39dde0a755a109146b68","tid":1171201,"uid":56625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7fa7caaf133c3a423534a576e00f3b1d8523f0d","tid":1171201,"uid":119337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"我整咗條有關小型房間嘅佈置影片，歡迎大家睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n我同好多師兄一樣，依家都喺香港住，間房亦唔算大。<br />\n<br />\n我成日留意其他師兄嘅自拍房間相同外國啲Youtubers嘅Setup 片，但一直未有時間同心機執房。<br />\n<br />\n最近終於的起心肝執過自己間房，但香港地寸金尺土，點樣喺有限嘅空間入面營造出自己風格實在係一個大考驗。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otJWgQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotJWgQF.png&h=ba16876b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己都睇咗唔少師兄嘅相，同外國嘅影片，先叫大致執好間房。<br />\n<br />\n但有個問題，就係外國大部分影片入面嘅房都大過我屋企個單位！所以有時覺得佢哋啲片嘅參考價值唔高！<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jZyi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jZyi4i.png&h=6c5d10fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我決定拍條片，將自己房間嘅佈置分享畀大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AAqN4PwXp5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAAqN4PwXp5Q&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=9f0bebf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AAqN4PwXp5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n但我自己本身並唔專業，所以我都想收集大家嘅房間佈置，希望將細房/電腦枱(大房都可以)嘅設計同佈置都分享畀其他師兄睇。<br />\n<br />\n我知道有自貼post show 咗師兄自己嘅房，但不問自取，是為賊也。<br />\n<br />\n如果有大家有興趣，歡迎填一填Google Form方便自己(同我)整理(填幾多無所謂，當然愈詳盡愈好)，連埋相片(當然又係愈多愈清晰愈好啦)畀我。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/qoNWyZbFFmTNK3XE6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FqoNWyZbFFmTNK3XE6&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=2ef2d488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/qoNWyZbFFmTNK3XE6</a><br />\n若要在google form 上載圖片，請登入google，抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n或者直接填下面嘅問題，連埋相片SEND去我Gmail<br />\nthenewtechtube@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何意見，都歡迎喺下面或YouTube 留comment<br />\n<br />\n我知道香港地做呢啲唔容易，仲要叫人主動畀資料我做更加係難上加難。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果大家畀面，我都會盡量將所有submission整成片。不過我並唔係全職Youtuber，所以都需要啲時間，希望大家明白啦。<br />\n<br />\n最後，有興趣都可以follow 埋我Instagram (thenewtechtube), Facebook (The New TECH TUBE)同twitter(@thenewtechtube1)啊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQWtgQb88CdcZRO7IvXdYpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCQWtgQb88CdcZRO7IvXdYpg&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=4f0cf328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQWtgQb88CdcZRO7IvXdYpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thenewtechtube/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthenewtechtube%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=b0b76e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/thenewtechtube/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/The-New-TECH-TUBE-471911690015160/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThe-New-TECH-TUBE-471911690015160%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=ebb7ed05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/The-New-TECH-TUBE-471911690015160/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheNewTechTube1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheNewTechTube1&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=353fa8e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheNewTechTube1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRoom setup questionnaire (the more detailed, the better) 房間佈置問題(選填，愈詳盡愈好)<br />\n1. Email address電郵地址<br />\n<br />\n2. Name/nickname姓名/暱稱<br />\n<br />\n3. From(Country/territory)來自(國家/地區) <br />\n<br />\n4. Room approximate size (length*width*height)(Metre)房間大概尺寸(長*闊*高)(米)<br />\n<br />\n5. Decoration/ Theme Description房間佈置/主題簡介<br />\n<br />\n6. PC(Laptop) Specs電腦(手提電腦)規格<br />\nCASE 機箱: <br />\nMotherboard 底板: <br />\nCPU中央處理器 : <br />\nGraphics: 顯示卡： <br />\nRAM 記憶體: <br />\nSSD固態硬碟: <br />\nHDD 硬碟: <br />\nOthers 其他:<br />\n<br />\n7. Other Hardware其他硬件(可多於一個)<br />\nMonitor(s)螢幕：<br />\nKeyboard(s)鍵盤：<br />\nMouse(Mice)滑鼠：<br />\nHeadset(s)耳筒：<br />\nSpeaker(s)喇叭：<br />\nDesk桌:<br />\nChair椅：<br />\nOther (Please specify)其他(請註明)：<br />\n<br />\n8. Other Gaming Console(s)其他遊戲主機(可多於一個)<br />\n<br />\n9. Other Information (Please specify)其他資料(請註明)：<br />\n<br />\n10. Photo(suggest at least 3)相片(建議最少3張)："},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"Ps4,機箱 架 要鑽牆？幾錢？<br />\n電腦枱已經死link<br />\n我間房同巴打差唔多 但係放左4尺衣櫃4尺床<br />\n所以枱勁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"唔使鑽牆啊<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcMQB7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcMQB7h.jpg&h=fb5cda49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要放衣櫃，可以考慮買ikea隻吊櫃嚟放其他嘢，不過要鑽牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FR4e3NK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFR4e3NK.jpg&h=52dc82b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以買玻璃門嗰款"},{"pid":"24f6a54baf6182eb6fe7461f31491003dc936c76","tid":1171201,"uid":119337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5d5569ba9f343309832b7d26650d61b8ed7982f","tid":1171201,"uid":30307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dcc59934a0f0d927475e75e3f3c4dc38844a0d7","tid":1171201,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d21b9e2e13c278e5164345480b709ddd2763dd","tid":1171201,"uid":30307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"如果大d想放埋部琴入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加個琴係廳都冇心情練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前間房仲細 之後呀婆走左先用佢間房<br />\n衣櫃又大床又大 呢2樣我都唔洗咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己設計過成間房又大工程又要dum家私<br />\n成間房得呢part係自己搞自己設計擺位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補番圖 2700x2500<br />\n有冇巴打知邊到多家私睇 我黎黎去去都淨係識大果2間 款又少冇岩心水好難設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c78ooX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c78ooX.png&h=7a2e23bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都算係咁了<br />\n問傢私後生仔應該都唔識答你<br />\n睇下有無識人讀/做設計行業可能先會識呢啲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係睇完你張圖突然有個idea諗到 <br />\n你電腦背面啲牆紙都有啲舊 但換又好煩<br />\n同一大面空白<br />\n會唔會買個大相框裝張靚既相上去裝飾下？<br />\n感覺會靚啲同養眼啲<br />\n又無咁單調<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DP9raaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDP9raaF.png&h=ccbd2539&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pefqqJ1.png\" d